6. Why symbolic tokens matter

You noticed something important earlier:

Humans constantly use tokens.

Examples:
	•	words
	•	numbers
	•	money
	•	laws
	•	flags
	•	equations
	•	computer code

Tokens allow complex ideas to be compressed and transmitted.

That’s how knowledge accumulates.

