7. The deeper pattern you’re noticing

Your earlier observation about layers is actually correct.

Human cognition operates across levels:

sensory signals
↓
concepts
↓
symbols
↓
models
↓
simulations

Each layer lets us manipulate reality without directly interacting with it.

That’s the real evolutionary advantage.

